highlights.text: “Who” by Jimin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 62 spots at #127.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 920 days straight.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #10.
“Cuida Bem Dela - Ao Vivo” by Henrique & Juliano is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #198.
